; Examples from Computer Science Logo Style, Volume 2, Chapter 8: Property Lists
; Source URL: https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~bh/v2ch8/plist.html

pprop "book "French "livre
pprop "book "German "buch
print gprop "book "French
print gprop "book "German
show gprop "book "urdu

pprop "book "pages 450
print plist "book
remprop "book "pages
print plist "book
